💭 File System Port
💭 Defines the contract for all persistent storage operations

🐊 🗄 🍇
  💭 Lists directory entries at the specified path
  ❗️ 📂 path 🔡 recursive 👌 ➡️ 🔡
  
  💭 Reads the full content of a file
  ❗️ 📖 path 🔡 ➡️ 🔡
  
  💭 Writes (overwrites) content to a file
  ❗️ 💿 path 🔡 content 🔡 ➡️ 🔡
  
  💭 Applies a search/replace diff to a file
  ❗️ 🔄 path 🔡 diff 🔡 ➡️ 🔡
  
  💭 Searches for a specific pattern within files
  ❗️ 🔍 path 🔡 search 🔡 ➡️ 🔡
🍉
